  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you can become incorporeal. <br />While incorporeal you can pass through any solid non-chakra-based matter and cannot be harmed by Ninjutsu, Taijutsu or Bukijutsu. <br />This includes Class mod Arts that would require physical interaction by any means. <br />A creature can only remain incorporeal until the beginning of their next turn.</p>",
